At this point,

17
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,470
will you still keep hiding it?

18
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,840
Grandmother,

19
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,470
the child Bingqing carries

20
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:17,640
is mine.

21
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:18,640
You...

22
00:01:21,540 --> 00:01:24,340
=Episode 20=
=Heir to the Throne=

23
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,430
Is there something you'd like to say?

24
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,040
No matter who asks,

25
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,390
you must insist firmly

26
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,190
the child you carry

27
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,520
is mine.

28
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,550
