My Lady.

135
00:10:01,610 --> 00:10:02,690
You're expecting, My Lady.

136
00:10:03,990 --> 00:10:05,610
My Lady, you're expecting.

137
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,790
Stay out of this.

138
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:40,720
Miss Jiang.

139
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,990
Where is Xiao Jingchu?

140
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,040
Has he left the palace?

141
