Are you all right?

142
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,350
Lord Xiao has come out now.

143
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,200
He's fine.

144
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,590
But he has official duties

145
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,440
to attend to.

146
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,630
So he sent me to bring your meal.

147
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,800
That's not the truth.

148
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:01,000
Lord Xiao...

149
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:03,810
